BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0dXte2B8shMljt9rCxpIW
SUMMARY:Loose Cannons 2026
DTSTAMP:20260330T060558Z
DTSTART:20260416T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Loose Cannons is Seattle improv at its most unpredictable. Ever
	y performance at Unexpected Productions in Pike Place Market is a one-of-a
	-kind experience: exciting\\\, unexpected\\\, a little dangerous\\\, and a
	lways ridiculously fun. This is the show where anything can happen and usu
	ally does. \\nPart One: Part One: The night kicks off with a unique perfor
	mance\\\, setting the performers in a new format with special guest improv
	isers showcasing their signature style or a never-before-seen format. Your
	 suggestions fuel the fire\\\, and the improvisers will ignite the stage\\
	\, bringing your ideas to life. \\nPart Two: The second half launches from
	 a single audience suggestion\\\, setting the performers in motion. It mig
	ht start with a song\\\, a monologue\\\, or a rapid-fire group connection 
	game. Whatever emerges will inspire spontaneous stories\\\, surprising twi
	sts\\\, and big comedic swings. \\nLoose Cannons is fueled by audience ide
	as\\\, fearless performers\\\, and the thrill of not knowing what happens 
	next. You light the fuse. They run with it. What they create is entirely u
	p to you.\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/loose-cannons-202
	6/2026-04-16/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/loose-cannons-2026/2026-04-
	16/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ZTM55jCrvGwgQ2uu9H8JE
SUMMARY:Spellbound: An Improvised Romantasy
DTSTAMP:20260330T060558Z
DTSTART:20260417T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Epic fantasy meets heart-pounding romance in a one-night-only i
	mprovised saga.\\n\\n\\n\\nSpellbound is a bold\\\, fun\\\, fully improvis
	ed romantasy where epic fantasy and big feelings take center stage. Inspir
	ed by books like A Court of Thorns and Roses and Fourth Wing\\\, our impro
	visers build a brand-new magical world on the spot using your ideas. \\nEx
	pect dramatic romance\\\, dangerous magic\\\, surprising twists\\\, and ch
	aracters who fall hard\\\, mess up spectacularly\\\, and make very questio
	nable choices in the name of love. It is playful\\\, passionate\\\, audien
	ce-powered storytelling with high stakes and zero scripts. Every show is a
	 fresh fantasy adventure that only happens once.\n\nhttps://www.unexpected
	productions.org/event/spellbound-an-improvised-romantasy/2026-04-17/\n\nFr
	om Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/spellbound-an-improvised-ro
	mantasy/2026-04-17/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
